February 11,2020.

The 18th day of the first lunar month.

The 20th day of the city closure in Wuhan.

Day 19 of the closure of the gate of Heaven.

I wrote a suicide note in 2012, but it became a gimmick. Staples Center, who had promised to cheer for Bryant at the time, seems naive. In the face of inscrutable fortune, the efforts of mankind seem vulnerable. Today, I will not allow those false delusions, seriously say a few nonsense.

1. It all boils down to three questions: What purpose, what means, and how it will be defined; and (who you are, where you came from, and where you will go.)

2. Love is meaning, meaning is love. Love can make you resonate with the world. In the increasingly absurd and virtual limited space, this is the only access to an infinite life of belonging and answer.

3. The principal contradiction between man and the world boils down to the slow evolution of the human body.

4. Imagination is the core competency. There's an English book called The Sense of Style, and The author mentions a word called The curse of knowledge. Once we know something, it's hard to imagine not knowing it.

5, the world is cold and warm, only from cross. "Ninety percent of your diseases are cured by your immune system, " the physician said. "heal occasionally; help often; comfort always. ".

6. When you don't live for eternity, you are completely free. You can't lose something you never got, unless it was your obsession; once you got it you won't lose it again unless you choose to throw it away.

7. Give more than you get. To learn is to do good. You know, it's all right to want to kill. Emancipating the Seek truth from facts, keeping up with the Times. Let go of your preconceptions and believe and act as if you have now achieved what you want.

8. The end is redemption, and there's a Deadline. Like all this crap I write every day, I have to turn it in by midnight tomorrow.

9. Live in the moment, but don't live for it. It's like I write all this crap every day, but it's not for today.

10. Don't let my eyes and my words see the world for you, so that you can only see the world I see, and anyone can only serve as your reference and sample;

11. Come to my funeral if you can't make it to my wedding.

12. Don't try to revive me without my consent.
